Minority representation for all Appointed Officers, Boards, Commissions,
Committees and Agencies shall be determined in accordance with the provisions
of Section [[9-167a|https://www.cga.ct.gov/current/pub/chap_146.htm#sec_9-167a]]
of the Connecticut General Statutes.